{"tid":1566943,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"香 港 國 旗 設 計 方 案","createTime":"2019-09-13T22:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T05:46:47.000Z","uid":225098,"like":8,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ab5dfef689a637a206d534bc67f15d10f8ca3659","tid":1566943,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZOn0DF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZOn0DF.jpg&h=f5f60a06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">拎住珍珠嘅獅子：</span><br />\n珍珠代表東方之珠，獅子代表英國，意思感謝英國嘅管治令香港成為東方之珠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五把黃遮砌成洋紫荊圖案：</span><br />\n洋紫荊係香港國花，黃遮紀念為香港獨立建國嘅抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帆船：</span><br />\n象徵香港十分注重海上貿易<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">城垛：</span><br />\n紀念1941年香港攻防戰同香港獨立戰爭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">白藍底色：</span><br />\n白色代表和平、廉潔同正義；藍色代表天空同海洋，象徵自由同主權"},{"pid":"c335164e6c12311affa0553ff87ca0810d8e69c2","tid":1566943,"uid":225098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:21:36.000Z","msg":"個人認為最重要係順眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199add0792177914980452fcac3f8a03ce344389","tid":1566943,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:22:40.000Z","msg":"無gear?"},{"pid":"02148ebebadac7decbf337525d6ce7d4da9756bb","tid":1566943,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:23:30.000Z","msg":"獅子加個豬嘴ok?"},{"pid":"1c1a8edd85bd3a91046f3eb188eecb0858f37e4f","tid":1566943,"uid":225098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"02148ebebadac7decbf337525d6ce7d4da9756bb","tid":1566943,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:23:30.000Z","msg":"獅子加個豬嘴ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T22:25:43.000Z","msg":"我覺得黃遮其實已經好帶到個意思出嚟，咁樣會Over咗，而且英國佬帶住個豬嘴<img s